snippet.title: JETT: Given Time - Showcase with Dev Commentary
snippet.description: A showcase of what's in store in Given Time, the new campaign coming to JETT: The Far Shore + Given Time on PlayStation and PC on January 31st 2023, featuring dev commentary from creative director Craig D. Adams of Superbrothers A/V.
